---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
import Title from "../shared/Title.astro";
import BtnLink from "../shared/BtnLink.astro";
---

<section id="features" class="bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 py-20">
    <Container className="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1 flex midmd:w-7/12 lg:w-1/2 flex-col">
            <Title>
                The Value Builder Path
            </Title>
            <Paragraph className="mt-8">
                <strong>Our Flagship Strategic Program</strong>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph className="mt-2">
                The Value Builder Path is a 6-month, CEPA-aligned program designed to help business owners intentionally build enterprise value. The focus is on clarity, owner independence, and strengthening the drivers that make a business worth more, whether an exit or transition is planned or not.
            </Paragraph>
            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-heading-3 font-medium">
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">
                        &checkmark;
                    </span>
                    <span class="font-bold">Comprehensive Business & Financial Diagnostic</span> to establish a value range, assess transferability, and identify key value drivers and gaps.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">
                        &checkmark;
                    </span>
                    <span class="font-bold">Owner Dependence & Operational Assessment</span> to reduce risk and strengthen systems.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">
                        &checkmark;
                    </span>
                    <span class="font-bold">Value Driver Action Plan</span> prioritizing initiatives that increase durability, cash flow, and scalability.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">
                        &checkmark;
                    </span>
                    <span class="font-bold">Strategic Direction & KPI Framework</span> aligning daily decisions with long-term value.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">
                        &checkmark;
                    </span>
                    <span class="font-bold">Execution & Accountability Support</span> ensuring progress is intentional and measurable.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto midmd:max-w-none lg:mx-0  lg:pr-10 xl:pr-2 flex-1 flex w-11/12 midmd:w-5/12 lg:w-1/2 midmd:h-auto">
            <div class="w-full h-80 sm:h-96 midmd:h-full relative">
                <div class="absolute rotate-45 -left-5 md:-left-10 lg:-left-20 xl:-left-24 p-1 top-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-400 blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
                <div class="absolute  p-1 -top-4 md:-top-10 right-0 w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-400 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-60"></div>
                
                <span class="absolute w-full aspect-[16/5] -skew-x-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-primary-400 opacity-40 blur-2xl left-0 bottom-0"></span>
                <img src={"/images/undraw_Developer_activity.png"} alt="banner image" 
                width="1240" height="1385"
                class=" w-auto rounded-3xl left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 absolute bottom-0 max-h-full" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
    <Container className="mt-8 flex">
        <div class="mx-auto">
            <div class="lg:min-w-max flex items-center sm:w-max w-full pb-6 lg:pb-0 border-b border-box-bg lg:border-0 px-6 lg:px-0">
                <BtnLink text="Book Your Free Discovery Call" href="https://thecompassgroup.zohobookings.com/#/thecompassgroup" className="flex justify-center w-full sm:w-max" variant="primary"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>